This paper deals with analyzing the compatibility of Android apps with different platform versions, which falls under the category of software engineering (cs.SE). It also involves analyzing the bytecode of the apps, which is related to programming languages (cs.PL). The paper also discusses potential security vulnerabilities in apps, which could be categorized under cybersecurity (cs.CR) and systems (cs.SY). Finally, the paper uses machine learning techniques to analyze the dataset, which could be related to machine learning (cs.LG).
